# Dante — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of Dante](dante.png)

**what —** The pilgrim who walks down through Hell, up the Mount, and home to the stars.

**why —** To be saved, and to bring back the map for everyone else.

**how —** Led first by reason, then by grace, one trembling foot before the next.

**where —** From the dark wood to the Empyrean — through all three realms.

